==联邦与州代理事务==
[[美国邮政署|美国邮政署]]经营着迈阿密邮局。迈阿密邮政总局位于西北第72大街2200号，是[[迈阿密-戴德县|迈阿密-戴德县]]位置较偏僻的地方，毗邻[[迈阿密国际机场|迈阿密国际机场]]<ref>"[http://usps.whitepages.com/service/post_office/2614?p=5&s=FL&service_name=post_office&z=Miami Post Office Location - MIAMI] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20120718212046/http://usps.whitepages.com/service/post_office/2614?p=5&s=FL&service_name=post_office&z=Miami |date=2012-07-18 }}." ''[[United_States_Postal_Service|United States Postal Service]]''. Retrieved on May 5, 2009.</ref>。

